axis of the hinge pin and parallel to the hinge face plate such that the hinge plates are not compressed against each
other. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
S4.4.3.3 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Load Test Three.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
